OL,3,GSouth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FSome early brightness in the
OL,6,Feast, otherwise another rather grey
OL,7,Fstart with patchy rain or drizzle,
OL,8,Fespecially over the moors. A few
OL,9,Fbreaks developing by the afternoon,
OL,10,Fbut further outbreaks of rain likely
OL,11,Fin the west. Winds strengthening later.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FA band of heavy rain and
OL,14,Fstrong winds will move eastwards this
OL,15,Fevening. Rain clearing during the
OL,16,Fearly hours allowing some clearer
OL,17,Fspells and a few showers to follow.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
